@startuml
title DropPilot Watch Runtime Flow

actor User
participant "useAppModel" as App
participant "usePriorityOrchestration" as Prio
participant "watchEngine\nreducer" as Engine
participant "useTargetDrops\n(inventory view)" as Drops
participant "useChannels" as Channels
participant "useWatchPing" as Ping
participant "watchStallRecovery\nhelpers" as Stall
participant "electronAPI.twitch\n(IPC)" as Twitch

== Target + Priority ==
App -> Prio: computeNextActiveTargetGame(...)
note right of Prio
Strict priority guard:
if current target is actively watched
and still actionable, do not preempt
immediately.
end note
Prio --> App: activeTargetGame
App -> Engine: selectVisibleTargetGame(activeTargetGame)
Engine --> App: targetGame (hidden when suppressed)
App -> Drops: computeTargetDrops(targetGame, watching, inventory)
Drops --> App: activeDropInfo + canWatchTarget

== Channels ==
App -> Channels: fetchChannels(targetGame)
Channels -> Twitch: tracker channels request
Twitch --> Channels: channel list
Channels --> App: prioritized channels + auto-switch decision
App -> Channels: setWatchingFromChannel(...)

== Watch Ping Loop ==
loop every ~59s (+ jitter)
  Ping -> Twitch: watch(channelId, login, streamId)
  Twitch --> Ping: ok / error
  Ping --> App: watchStats + bumpStats(minutes)
end

== Stall Detection ==
App -> Stall: evaluateNoProgressStall(...)
alt shouldRecover == false
  Stall --> App: keep/reset tracker only
else shouldRecover == true
  alt channel-level recovery possible
    App -> Stall: pickStallRecoveryChannel(...)
    Stall --> App: nextChannel
    App -> Channels: setWatchingFromChannel(nextChannel)
  else no channel or retry budget exhausted
    App -> Prio: getNextPriorityTargetGame(current)
    Prio --> App: next game (actionable-first, fallback to next priority)
    App -> App: clearWatching + setAutoSelectEnabled(true)
    App -> Engine: dispatch(watch/stall_stop, activeTargetGame)
  end
end

== Suppression Lifecycle ==
loop on sync + hold-expire timer
  App -> Engine: dispatch(sync(activeTargetGame, watchingGame, now))
  alt suppressionReason == manual-stop
    Engine --> App: clear when another game is watched
  else suppressionReason == stall-stop
    alt hold window active
      Engine --> App: keep suppressed
    else hold expired
      alt still watching same stalled game
        Engine --> App: keep suppressed
      else idle or watching different game
        Engine --> App: clear suppressed target
      end
    end
  end
end

== Manual Actions ==
User -> App: manual start watching(channel)
App -> Engine: dispatch(watch/manual_start)
User -> App: stop watching
App -> Engine: dispatch(watch/stop, activeTargetGame)

@enduml
